  +openl2tp-1.8.ebuild, files/openl2tpd.initd:
  Use dns daemon too.

*openl2tp-1.8.ebuild (28 Nov 2010)

  28 Nov 2010; Andrew Savchenko <bircoph@gmail.com> 
